<br>
It has great potential. <br>
<br>
I bought it and am playing it now, EVEN KNOWING that it still has a lot of bugs to fix, and several balancing issues (yes yes, nerfs are coming for sure). But despite this, the game can only get much better. <br>
<br>
It's a player driven economy.  <br>
<br>
The PvP is &quot;just right&quot; for my taste. You dont get too much of it. And you dont get too little.  It's just right in the middle. <br>
<br>
Role playing is a blast.  There are tons of tiny little features that actually help encourage role playing.  <br>
<br>
If you are an impatient person and you have a spasm every time you encounter a bug, then I suggest that you hold off from buying this game.  Maybe buy the game 2 or 3 months from now. <br>
<br>
